    • settleBGBills

      public void settleBGBills()
      Settles all bills paid by MSP that have an explanatory code of 'BG' Bills of this type were paid an amount that was different from the original bill amount. Therefore, an 'Internal Adjustment' is applied to the difference in order to ensure that the amount owing is $0.00.
